## ğŸ¯ Overview

Crabster Technology's website is a high-performance, component-based static site built with modern web standards. Featuring a modular architecture, dynamic review system, and polished animations, it delivers a premium user experience while maintaining exceptional performance and simplicity.

### Why Crabster?

- ğŸš€ **Lightning Fast** â€” No build process, instant loading
- ğŸ§© **Modular Design** â€” Reusable HTML components for easy maintenance
- ğŸ“± **Fully Responsive** â€” Seamless experience across all devices
- âœ¨ **Interactive** â€” Smooth animations, custom cursor, real-time reviews
- ğŸ¨ **Polished UI** â€” Modern glassmorphism effects with Tailwind CSS

