## âœ¨ Key Features

### ğŸ§± Component Architecture
- **Modular HTML Components** â€” Separate files for header, hero, services, products, reviews, contact, and footer
- **Easy Maintenance** â€” Update individual components without touching the entire codebase
- **Reusable Across Projects** â€” Drop components into other sites

### ğŸ¨ Visual Excellence
- **Smooth Animations** â€” AOS (Animate On Scroll) integration
- **Particle Effects** â€” Dynamic background particles in hero section
- **Custom Cursor** â€” Interactive cursor following with smooth transitions
- **Glassmorphism UI** â€” Modern frosted glass effects on cards and navigation
- **Scroll Progress Bar** â€” Visual feedback for page navigation
- **Decorative Shapes** â€” Floating geometric elements

### ğŸ“± Responsive Design
- **Mobile-First** â€” Optimized for all screen sizes
- **Slide-Out Navigation** â€” Touch-friendly mobile menu
- **Sticky Header** â€” Glass effect header that stays visible on scroll
- **Adaptive Layouts** â€” Content reflows gracefully

### â­ Dynamic Reviews System
- **Real-Time Reviews** â€” Backend API integration
- **Star Rating System** â€” Interactive 5-star rating input and display
- **Skeleton Loaders** â€” Smooth loading states
- **Pagination** â€” "Load More" functionality for better performance
- **Form Validation** â€” Client-side validation with helpful error messages
- **Service Filtering** â€” Reviews categorized by service type

### ğŸ¥ Media Handling
- **Graceful Video Fallback** â€” Automatic fallback to images if video fails
- **Lazy Loading** â€” Videos and images load only when needed
- **Optimized Delivery** â€” Compressed assets for fast loading

