## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

### Core Technologies
- **HTML5** â€” Semantic markup with component fragments
- **CSS3** â€” Modern styling with custom properties
- **Vanilla JavaScript** â€” No framework dependencies, pure JS for performance

### Styling
- **Tailwind CSS 3.x** â€” Utility-first CSS via CDN
- **Custom CSS Modules:**
  - `main.css` â€” Global variables, utilities, overrides
  - `animations.css` â€” Cursor, float, and decorative animations
  - `components.css` â€” Component-specific styles
  - `feedback.css` â€” Review system styling
  - `products.css` â€” Product cards and video presentation

### JavaScript Modules
- `navbar.js` â€” Header, mobile menu, sticky behavior
- `cursor.js` â€” Custom cursor interactions
- `products.js` â€” Video loading and error handling
- `reviews.js` â€” Review API, star ratings, rendering, pagination
- `app.js` â€” Scroll progress, theme initialization

### Visual Libraries
- **AOS.js** â€” Scroll-triggered animations
- **Particles.js** â€” Particle background effects
- **Font Awesome** â€” Icon library

